{"tid":2072272,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如果表白失敗...","createTime":"2020-06-20T12:53:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T02:16:22.000Z","uid":319228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3dc467960f43b725ae778b89748251522deba02c","tid":2072272,"uid":319228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:53:52.000Z","msg":"仲有冇得做番朋友？<br />\n兩個之間嘅感覺會唔會唔同咗，定係會直接end game或者變到好尷尬？<br />\n暗示、比人feel到、比人無視都當失敗。"},{"pid":"6874f6e63fa519b3518faf0799ee2d14ce37a258","tid":2072272,"uid":305631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T13:05:34.000Z","msg":"巴打諗住表白？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b18477fbc79e4e83fab064964d8946025a384b2a","tid":2072272,"uid":240392,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"3dc467960f43b725ae778b89748251522deba02c","tid":2072272,"uid":319228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:53:52.000Z","msg":"仲有冇得做番朋友？<br />\n兩個之間嘅感覺會唔會唔同咗，定係會直接end game或者變到好尷尬？<br />\n暗示、比人feel到、比人無視都當失敗。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T13:40:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ee2a3a19d941db6854177fadf8ffdc4ff18c15","tid":2072272,"uid":84741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T13:50:58.000Z","msg":"預咗冇咗個朋友啦"},{"pid":"710baf20d9efdabe9432361a16e29fbb0040218f","tid":2072272,"uid":170176,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T13:54:23.000Z","msg":"通常都好難番番去之前咁frd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔多唔少都會有啲芥蒂<br />\n好大機會對方可能會避住你<br />\n<br />\n巴打諗住暗示定直接表白先？"},{"pid":"569cf763e6b9d71154ad0bb29c359ce9bfbc2a79","tid":2072272,"uid":349439,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T13:58:13.000Z","msg":"可以，但係好難<br />\n如果佢真心當你朋友又唔係收兵嘅人，一般而言佢都會想同你保持一段距離，廢事俾錯覺你（同埋會有啲尷尬）<br />\n就算你說服到佢可以做返朋友，你都首先要諗清楚自己嘅定位<br />\n究竟你係一表完即刻放低到佢當佢100%朋友，定係諗住做住fd先以後等機會或者日久生情<br />\n我覺得冇咩人可以做到前者<br />\n如果係後者嘅話，就睇你自己控唔控制到自己內心<br />\n人一旦有付出其實或多或少會期望對方俾到回報你，會唔多甘心只係做到朋友，除非你特別忍得"},{"pid":"134521e2fcc6120dbd8db87f4344eaaebd846de3","tid":2072272,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T13:58:37.000Z","msg":"除非你真係比對方感覺到你放低咗<br />\n如果唔係一定尷尬<br />\n放低咗+比佢feel到你變咗另一個人先會再有機會<br />\n無錯係要先放低<br />\n呢一點大部份人都做唔到"},{"pid":"c7c678266b93b7a7d01c8846e8064890f6cc4b09","tid":2072272,"uid":143321,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T14:00:50.000Z","msg":"溝女唔使表白<br />\n表白9 成衰硬..."},{"pid":"c3fd2e5580077f3a8cb05947b38be9ac32de0520","tid":2072272,"uid":149494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c7c678266b93b7a7d01c8846e8064890f6cc4b09","tid":2072272,"uid":143321,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T14:00:50.000Z","msg":"溝女唔使表白<br />\n表白9 成衰硬..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T14:04:46.000Z","msg":"只有一種情況可以表白<br />\n就係100%知道食硬<br />\n否則表條毛咩，表白即係迫條女收你皮<br />\n邊有人咁撚蠢"},{"pid":"213a3854dbbde2efa64a1c1e35453d6e28a9bccb","tid":2072272,"uid":149494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T14:09:16.000Z","msg":"樓主同對方斷絕聯絡幾個月先啦"},{"pid":"8830ec23370755a593647306a2e17ebc7cc7c918","tid":2072272,"uid":188511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7c678266b93b7a7d01c8846e8064890f6cc4b09","tid":2072272,"uid":143321,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T14:00:50.000Z","msg":"溝女唔使表白<br />\n表白9 成衰硬..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T14:12:54.000Z","msg":"十分認同 係鐘意你嘅 又點會要你特登表白<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47614c300eeadefb09e0bc7f7e2a9931a49c844f","tid":2072272,"uid":263534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T14:15:57.000Z","msg":"朋友大把，點解要留佢<br />\n做人乾脆啲唔得就斬纜咪拖住自己錯失其他機會"},{"pid":"d4f3d75c84dc80deeae57bc7f6c1fab551779ea2","tid":2072272,"uid":143321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{